criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria for obese group:

          -  BMI > 30 g/m2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  antibiotic treatment within last three months;

          -  food restrictions due to allergies, any kind of food intolerance,
             veganism/vegetarianism or other extremes in food consumption practices;

          -  chronic illnesses;

          -  current pregnancy or breastfeeding

          -  travel to subtropical or tropical regions within one month before the study.
